"><mn>21</mn></math>, which is greater than <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"17\"><mn>17</mn></math>; when <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"x equals 5\"><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>5</mn></math>, the corresponding value of <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"y\"><mi>y</mi></math> is <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"35\"><mn>35</mn></math>, which is greater than <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"31\"><mn>31</mn></math>; when <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"x equals 8\"><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>8</mn></math>, the corresponding value of <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"y\"><mi>y</mi></math> is <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"56\"><mn>56</mn></math>, which is greater than <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"52\"><mn>52</mn></math>. Of the given choices, only choice D gives values of <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"x\"><mi>x</mi></math> and their corresponding values of <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"y\"><mi>y</mi></math> that are all solutions to the given inequality.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Choice A is incorrect and may result from conceptual or calculation errors.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Choice B is incorrect and may result from conceptual or calculation errors.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Choice C is incorrect and may result from conceptual or calculation errors.</p>",
